{"type": "article", "id": 30113, "title": "用圆环装的酒，样子还挺酷的｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-07-25T23:06:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 30625, "name": "Lightovo"}, {"id": 30626, "name": "Nursery Works"}, {"id": 30627, "name": "Monowear Design"}, {"id": 30628, "name": "Digital Fish"}, {"id": 30629, "name": "Tadeáš Podracký"}, {"id": 30630, "name": "Alexander Kanygin"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016080417093262A7pxyGSQtjErDb.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Umbrella table &amp; stool by Tadeáš Podracký</h3><p>捷克设计师 <a href=\"http://tadeaspodracky.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tadeáš Podracký</a> 经常在自己的作品中融合来自世界各地的不同技艺，他最新的 Umbrella 桌椅系列就借鉴了余杭地区油纸伞的结构，并使用中国的青铜作为材料。Podracký 在余杭地区探访了油纸伞的工房，对伞进行了解构处理并按照不同的顺序进行组装。在最后的成品中可以清楚地看到重组的伞结构，带有浓厚的中国风情。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230610qTAzfBvgr8p7iO64.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230609j7xlGJ6HUn0WAhC3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230609uOeWdEnRK4p36D27.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607252306093lzQCwiZnhm0G7tY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230609pDhuC4aUFB7jNP3i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230609RXB0m7hMG1dYeV4x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Milo Lamp by Lightovo</h3><p>你的床头灯也能变成展示花草的家饰，波兰设计工作室 Lightovo 推出的 Milo Lamp 就是一款能够摆放花器的灯具，不仅可以放在桌上也可以当作吊灯使用。金属灯罩下方连接着一个玻璃罩子，两边各有一个小洞，通过它可以塞入不大的花草，浇起水来也非常方便。简洁的造型适用于各种居家环境，温暖的灯光与绿意盎然的植物相结合，带给人一种平和舒适的感觉。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/Lightovo\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 201.69 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230547lPZqB0XSfv1YLw5n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.280000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230547odYwnbj0yMcHsALZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230548FkLp30whbtyux49T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607252305481SWd9ctvOHJ84kbP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.462500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230547p0cY7O2vbFfgNUdh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.318750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ami Rocker by Nursery Works</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.nurseryworks.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nursery Works</a> 的设计师们这次脑洞大开，将两件为人带来舒适感的家具结合在了一起 ，打造了一件兼具沙发和摇椅功能的家具 Ami Rocker。烤漆的钢管支架上有着非常流畅的曲线，依靠底部精心设计的弧度维持着平衡。支架上摆放着柔软的羊毛坐垫和一个摇篮，适合大人和孩子一起坐在上面轻轻摇晃着度过温馨的亲子时光。由于采用了模块化的设计，摇篮也可以换为坐垫，改造成一款双人沙发，有着很强的实用性。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.nurseryworks.net/ami-rocker\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1250 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230522cxDzRNSdAv7WtPCY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230522YGD5e0QTtodW91Af.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607252305223uLjtqRNEUfiHOWJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230522J5r2RQelM0nHapDy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230522i0npJkg29XT8OIWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230522zH5NIwdf93oiUbQu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MTO by Alexander Kanygin</h3><p>来自俄罗斯的 <a href=\"http://alexanderkanygin.tictail.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Kanygin</a> 利用橡木制作了一款名为 MTO 的收纳系统，乍一看似乎和市面上常见的收纳盒并没有什么太大的差别，但只要做略微的调整你就会发现它不仅仅是个分割出几个空间的收纳工具。实际上它由两个木盒所组成，通过橡皮圈相连。木盒的每一面都被设计了不同的功能，根据需要进行翻转组合后，可以同时用做零钱罐、笔筒、绕线器等等，能够满足人们的日常需求，无论是放在办公室还是家中的玄关处都很合适。这是它的<a href=\"http://alexanderkanygin.tictail.com/product/mto\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 13500 卢布。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230505wp0lu5oVvnGNCbEj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230505k0DAUYyZGiNceqp8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230505pI28otOWCqGPRaUf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230505QN8qseKbj40kRGrc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230505u3p8MZPi4mrvQkhX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230506vmd9PJ1niKfWTjU4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MonoCharge by Monowear Design</h3><p>想让充电的过程变得更加优雅？在 Monowear Design 的设计师眼中，你需要的可能不仅仅是“无线化”：经过精心的设计，一个可以根据需要灵活调整并且同时为手机和 Apple Watch 充电的 MonoCharge 充电座诞生了。MonoCharge 采用模块化设计，两个具有无线充电功能的组件通过磁性相结合。它就好像是积木一样，只需要转换不同的贴合面，MonoCharge 就能在不三种不同的造型之间切换，携带起来非常方便，你也可以把它当作手机或者平板设备的支架使用。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1843570774/monocharge-wireless-charging-reimagined\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 79 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607252304362faTwtdP7XrmsRLF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.882353\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230436GwPl85ItYmxJR41D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.511765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230436zltgI279DwHSeMPB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670165\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230436ZGNiIm2OcBVbJHus.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670181\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230436I28G6JtCmOQiDSWa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230437mFW3Ujulvhdk80Ar.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662669\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Oruka by Digital Fish</h3><p>初看到 Oruka 这两个一金一银的圆环时，你或许还以为是某种风格奇特的家饰。在约鲁巴语中 Oruka 意味着圆环，<a href=\"http://digitalfish.tv/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Digital Fish</a> 正是以此为灵感设计了这套琴酒和朗姆酒的概念包装，经过旋转才能顺利倒出酒来。除了大胆地舍弃传统的瓶装改用精致优雅的圆环容器之外，内侧还根据 shot 标上了刻度。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230359ULc9A0HFo3DSEu5B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230359o8iXlCpBenW76Uct.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230359Ef8oCIrTFGpnURqx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230359WoiVeIR92AFc0zXK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.900000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725230359HuLjWbVfsn0A1vGo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}